msgid "⚠️ Admin Tips"
msgstr "⚠️ Cussegls d'Administraschiun"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:45
msgid ""
"Never run in production with DEBUG enabled. Debug mode exposes internal "
"details and stack traces."
msgstr ""
"Mai executable en produzione cun DEBUG activà. Il modus Debug exploda "
"detagls interns e traces da stack."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:47
msgid ""
"Always deploy Grylli behind a reverse proxy (e.g. Caddy, Nginx, or Traefik) "
"and serve it over HTTPS. Sensitive user data must be encrypted in transit."
msgstr ""
"Deployar adina Grylli davos in proxy invers (p. ex. Caddy, Nginx, u Traefik)"
" e servirl sur HTTPS. Datas sensiblas da l'utilisader ston vegnir criptadas "
"durant il transit."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:50
msgid ""
"Ensure the data folder (database) is backed up regularly. Backups are stored"
" in the 'backups' folder."
msgstr ""
"Assegurar che la carpeta da datas (banca da datas) vegnia resguardada sin "
"tes ospitant"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:53
msgid ""
"The uploads folder is shared. To isolate attachments per user, configure "
"host-level directories and access controls."
msgstr ""
"Il dossier uploads è depleeat. Per isoler attatgaments par utilisaderades "
"che directivas da nivel, e controllas d'accesso."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:55
msgid ""
"To restore a backup: stop the container, replace the grylli.db file from a "
"backup, and restart."
msgstr ""
"Per restabilir ina copia da backup: termnar il conturner, remplazzar il "
"data/grylli.db cun ina ord la carpeta da backup e puspè lantschar il "
"conturner."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:56
msgid ""
"Admins cannot remove their own admin role to prevent accidental lockout."
msgstr ""
"Admins bod löslercrea. Sistire il admin hetir brie in pimirida da sì pro "
"planisar persecontran."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:58
